Thumbs.db

# Local Claude assistant context — kept out of git so contributors don't
# inherit operator examples specific to one deployment and personal
# preferences. Re-add the file (and remove this rule) when the project
# is ready to ship a public, generic version of these instructions.
CLAUDE.md
